Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roanapur...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Various gangs from around the\nworld fight for territory in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange balancing game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is a terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The outside of the building is unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right now we know that there are 32\nfatalities from among the embassy workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And when the wounded are added, there are 150 victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Currently the Zaire military is continuing its rescue efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}Right after the bombing, a terrorist organization calling themselves\nthe Protectors of the Islamic Front have taken credit for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a dirty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a job. Dutch says it's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a big last minute request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to "wake her the hell up", so I rushed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The job... from who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Triad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even offer a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this service, Dutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know we were a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know why we have a torpedo\nboat, don't you, Mr. Chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cold, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were burned out of our place and came straight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it human nature to at least offer a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was a tragedy, Chan-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say half of your offices are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got hit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the Russians?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always very friendly with Miss Balalaika...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Two-Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. We're about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cause of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that just shows it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took this from a stupid Bulgarian who\ntried to make a quick buck in my territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall giving permission to anyone but Yolanda\nfrom the Church of Violence to sell weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these guys misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were selling guns like they\nwere hot shrimps from a stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He misunderstood my warnings as a crazy joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally understood and made a deal\nwhen it was time to crush his balls like nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it turns out he had an interesting job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked on intelligence for Bulgaria, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is a comfortable place for folks like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally a guy like that is very useful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing with fire this time cost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What he offered us for the sake\nof his balls was this, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hiking charts for a certain amusing little group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The job they did right before us\nhas been on TV all damn morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The US Embassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dangerous one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balls-boy's real job was with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's full of folks who want Uncle Sam to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told one of those groups that they dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before they heard what it'd cost them, they told me to\N"get the hell out of here before your ass becomes roast."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is how I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"All right, then I'll go elsewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my offices flew all the way to Jordan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, as predicted, my ass nearly\nbecame a roast before I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Dutch, this is the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to deliver this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five teams will leave Roanapur at the\nsame time, with different destinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five cases but only one bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A feint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As insurance, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your goal is the Filipino base on Basilan Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit is two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my CIA contacts will leave Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days is too soon, Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning's embassy bombing\nwas the beginning of a chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two days the next schedule starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're done hiking there's\ngoing to be a new president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Sam came to me because their\nembassy blew up like the Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A getaway driver we hired will\ndeliver it to the base when you land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring our pay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're calculating expenses separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RPG!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. They sure are quick. They're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Are you safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your information's off, Chan-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This job's cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're going to have to pay the repair bill for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least escort you to the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been on the field in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your emergency exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way, Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand gre...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, Two-Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you hesitate, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chan's cleared the way. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting lax, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bark, Two-Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the nerves, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't see the big picture yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not compared to you. I'll just stick with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending a car. Get to the harbor with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to do a job that doesn't\ninvolve risking my life sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bitch, Dutch. We're about to do the hard part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you, Chan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get there don't forget the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The password is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our comrades have found the\ndelivery boys on the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take care of them near Bankantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This job should have been over with\nafter the bombing of the Triad office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no mood to judge the failures of our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mocked the "simple gangsters."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chan was a much smarter gangster than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"See the enemy you should respect,\nnot the enemy you despise."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words of Mao Tse-tung. You should study it, Ibraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lesson of a man who does not believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't believe in God either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my comrade, Takenaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should speed up the plan in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. The FBI has been watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we move now, the plan will be wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the five routes they've taken,\nthe first one to discount is over land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only leaves a sea route. Do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask a comrade commander\nin the Philippines for assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea route... I guess I'll have to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final step in changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is wide, and so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Triad is super cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chan can handle himself and has\ngreat style, but when it comes to jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nobody's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A torpedo boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chan's got some interesting friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've determined their path too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just as we predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I don't have to change my flight route.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to switch planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't do anything until I arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to confirm a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from Japan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you held your hand when you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on a family trip to Seb Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit far from Manilla if you're with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this isn't the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.36,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(400,15,400,15,400,20)}{\1aH&99&}{\bord2\shad0}{\p1}m 10 0 l 358 0 368 10 368 39 358 49 10 49 0 39 0 10 10 0{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.36,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-san is a Japanese comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People always say I look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are aloof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've seen me somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\move(103,505,103,460)\c&HFAFAFA&}Takenaka Masahiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got them, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The noisy little fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, bring me the Remington, and the Hydra API for ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've taken out the enemy's\neyes, but that might not be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, we'll be bait and charge towards Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you and Revy to get off at Zamboanga\nand use the Zodiac to get to Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibraha! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takenaka! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basilan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Our diversion team is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at their camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lighthouse's base is always the darkest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting here for the first blow\namong the local guerillas, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's the same for them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place an American imperialist agent can come\nand go is the anti-guerilla special operations camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right over the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Chan's next move. This is going to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the precursor to the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, this is an exchange of pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think there's something else in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be the ones that take the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is hard-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if you don't have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, once we deliver the papers we'll meet you at the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, I'll come get you when I lose the guys that are bitten on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys who fight for a cause are so damn persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Mr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Rock comes back from the bathroom tell him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is moving further north from Zamboanga coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they passed Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basilan is already behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe they will be heading north from Negros.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will continue pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening. They're coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Basilan, there's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a dinky-ass place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly six.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We took more time than expected to find a place to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The village should be right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a human-less ghost village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been martial law here for the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and the guerillas are shooting\nlead at each other day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here must have run away to a real city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from Lagoon, right? I heard that there were four of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why should I answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just me and him and a briefcase. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see your partner. Where's your guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's running around looking for a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know the difference between beer and Volvic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a time for jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fuck around I'll shoot you in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't get hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a little joke to break the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,super cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sense of humor is a little screwy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it was that bad for Mr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from the boss for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am Taishanfujun."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the god of death and punishment\nhere to bring down judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where you got the password,\nbut Boss Chan isn't an idiot or a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He prepared a new password for shitheads like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hopped into this parade with your ass hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting handled like this by a little girl, pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, you idiot! You fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunfire's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legarch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You relax too much before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to move until the gunfire dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she dies, no pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, work important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot shithead Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, lower your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the getaway driver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like an attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The military's left their camp, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there were four of you from Mr. Chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plans changed so it became two. Then one got captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going straight to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to finish this job and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's their base?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,North of village. Six miles. In the jungle yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to the base. We'll take care of them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your own damn ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or tell that to the cavalry, Mary Read.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job is take you to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get pay. No to all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner has the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it? "Understand you yes?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes it is" lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stain the seats, Shenhua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna do it, do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,English not good because I am real Taiwanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it not big deal if head separated from neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think the boss hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they aren't all together then it's us three idiots in this\ncar that's gonna have to do the twist in front of the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've formed an alliance. This\ncamp is under our command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... welcome to our demilitarized zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw what was inside the briefcase. It was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I did, I couldn't answer. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A straightforward answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, you should at least crack a joke. Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have time. We'll ask you slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this in Japanese, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to get involved in this kind of\nstuff, you need to be a little more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Japanese, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have you been doing this kind of job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to keep quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't hurt for similar people like us to be friendly to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the launderer's delivery boy arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Langley!
